---
title: Chermoula Chicken & Veggie Couscous with Garlic Dip
description: Who doesn’t like a bit of char on their chicken? This one gets a generous coating of our punchy chermoula spice blend before it crisps up in the pan until golden. Pair your succulent chicken with the colourful veggie-packed couscous and a sprinkling of toasted almonds for extra crunch.
